EINSTEIN GENERATIVE AI
Data Model for Generative AI Audit and Feedback

Understand and analyze your Einstein generative AI audit and feedback data using the appropriate data model objects (DMOs). Einstein generative AI audit and feedback data is streamed to a data lake object (DLO) in Data Cloud and then mapped to data model objects (DMO).

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Einstein generative AI is available in Lightning Experience. Setup for Einstein generative AI is available in Lightning Experience.
Available in: Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions with an Einstein for Sales, Einstein for Platform, or Einstein for Service add-on. To purchase the Einstein for Sales, Einstein for Platform, or Einstein for Service add-on, contact your Salesforce account executive.

Generative AI Audit and Feedback FlowChart

Einstein Generative AI App Generation DMO
A Data Cloud DMO that captures feature-specific changes made to the original generated text. The GenAIAppGeneration object has these attributes.
Einstein Generative AI Content Category DMO
A Data Cloud DMO that captures Einstein Trust Layer detector result values by detector type and sub-category. This DMO includes the safety and toxicity scores of output from the LLM. The GenAIContentCategory object has these attributes.
Einstein Generative AI Content Quality DMO
A Data Cloud DMO that captures if a request or response is safe or unsafe. The GenAIContentQuality object has these attributes.
Einstein Generative AI Feedback DMO
A Data Cloud DMO that captures feedback for a specific generation or part of a generation. The GenAIFeedback object has these attributes.
Einstein Generative AI Feedback Detail DMO
A Data Cloud DMO for details of user feedback. This DMO may include sensitive user data. The GenAIFeedbackDetail object has these attributes.
Einstein Generative AI Gateway Request DMO
A Data Cloud DMO that captures prompt input, request parameters, and model details and parameters. This DMO may include sensitive data.. The GenAIGatewayRequest object has these attributes.
Einstein Generative AI Gateway Request Tag DMO
A Data Cloud DMO that captures any custom data points as key-value pairs. The GenAIGatewatRequestTag object has these attributes.
Einstein Generative AI Gateway Response DMO
A Data Cloud DMO that enables joins between the GenAIRequest DMO and GenAIGenerations DMO. The GenAIGatewayResponse object has these attributes.
Einstein Generative AI Generations DMO
A Data Cloud DMO that captures generated responses returned for generation requests. This DMO also includes masked prompts if masking is enabled and may also include sensitive user data. The GenAIGeneration object has these attributes.
